Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["\<\
Analytical Multipole Eshelby Concentration Factors for a Sphere\
\>", "Title",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0001-0001-0001-000000000001"],

Cell["T. M. Nestor \[Dash] Research School of Earth Sciences, ANU", "Subtitle",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0001-0001-0001-000000000002"],

Cell["\<\
Derives closed-form rational expressions for the multipole Eshelby \
concentration factors E_n for elastic sphere scattering. In the static limit \
(\[Omega]\[Rule]0), Bessel functions collapse to power laws, making the Mie \
boundary problem purely algebraic. This yields exact E_n at any order n, \
generalizing the classical \[Alpha]_E (n=0) and \[Beta]_E (n=2) results.

The concentration factor relates full to Born scattering coefficients:
    a_n(full) = E_n \[CenterDot] a_n(Born)

Known results: E_0 = K_0/(K_0 + \[Alpha]_E \[CapitalDelta]K), E_1 = 1, \
E_2 = 1/(1 + \[Beta]_E \[CapitalDelta]\[Mu]/\[Mu]_0).
New: closed-form E_3, E_4, E_5 as rational functions of elastic moduli.\
\>", "Text",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0001-0001-0001-000000000003"],

(* ===== Section 1: Setup ===== *)

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["1. Setup & Parameters", "Section",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0002-0001-0001-000000000001"],

Cell["\<\
Clear all symbols. Define background elastic parameters matching the Python \
test suite: \[Alpha]=5000 m/s, \[Beta]=3000 m/s, \[Rho]=2500 kg/m\
\[ThreeSuperior]. Work symbolically with \[Lambda]0, \[Mu]0, \[CapitalDelta]\
\[Lambda], \[CapitalDelta]\[Mu], \[CapitalDelta]\[Rho], then substitute \
numerical values at the end.\
\>", "Text",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0002-0001-0001-000000000002"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{"ClearAll", "[", "\"\<Global`*\>\"", "]"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", " ",
   RowBox[{"Derived", " ", "quantities"}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"K0", "=",
    RowBox[{"\[Lambda]0", "+",
     RowBox[{"2",
      RowBox[{"\[Mu]0", "/", "3"}]}]}]}], ";"}]}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[Nu]0", "=",
   RowBox[{"\[Lambda]0", "/",
    RowBox[{"(",
     RowBox[{"2",
      RowBox[{"(",
       RowBox[{"\[Lambda]0", "+", "\[Mu]0"}], ")"}]}], ")"}]}]}],
  ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", " ",
   RowBox[{"Interior", " ", "moduli"}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"\[Lambda]1", "=",
    RowBox[{"\[Lambda]0", "+", "d\[Lambda]"}]}], ";"}]}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[Mu]1", "=",
   RowBox[{"\[Mu]0", "+", "d\[Mu]"}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"K1", "=",
   RowBox[{"\[Lambda]1", "+",
    RowBox[{"2",
     RowBox[{"\[Mu]1", "/", "3"}]}]}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"dK", "=",
   RowBox[{"d\[Lambda]", "+",
    RowBox[{"2",
     RowBox[{"d\[Mu]", "/", "3"}]}]}]}], ";"}]}], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[1]:=",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0002-0001-0001-000000000003"]
}, Open  ]],

(* ===== Section 2: Static Mie Solve ===== *)

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["2. Static Mie Boundary Problem", "Section",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0003-0001-0001-000000000001"],

Cell["\<\
In the static limit, spherical Bessel functions become power laws:
  j_n(z) \[Rule] z^n / (2n+1)!!,  h_n(z) \[Rule] -i(2n-1)!! / z^(n+1)
We substitute these into the P-wave and S-wave field functions from \
sphere_scattering.py, build the 4\[Times]4 boundary matrix, and solve for \
the scattered P coefficient A_n.

Rather than try to factor out powers of \[Omega] symbolically (which fails \
because \[Omega] appears inside square roots for wavespeeds), we use \
Mathematica\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Series[] to expand A_n in powers of \[Omega] \
and extract the leading coefficient. The concentration factor E_n is then the \
ratio of the full leading coefficient to its Born (linearized) limit.\
\>", "Text",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0003-0001-0001-000000000002"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", " ",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     "P", "-", "wave", " ", "fields", " ", "from", " ", "\[Phi]"}], "=",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"zn",
      RowBox[{"(", "kr", ")"}]}], " ",
     RowBox[{"Pn", ".", " ",
      RowBox[{"Returns", " ", "{",
       RowBox[{"ur", ",", " ", "ut", ",", " ", "srr", ",", " ", "srt"}],
       "}"}]}]}]}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"pF", "[",
     RowBox[{
     "n_", ",", "k_", ",", "r_", ",", "\[Lambda]_", ",", "\[Mu]_", ",",
      "zn_", ",", "znp_"}], "]"}], ":=",
    RowBox[{"{",
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"k", " ", "znp"}], ",",
      RowBox[{"zn", "/", "r"}], ",",
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-",
         RowBox[{"(",
          RowBox[{"\[Lambda]", "+",
           RowBox[{"2", "\[Mu]"}]}], ")"}]}], " ",
        RowBox[{"k", "^", "2"}], " ", "zn"}], "-",
       RowBox[{"4", "\[Mu]", " ", "k", " ",
        RowBox[{"znp", "/", "r"}]}], "+",
       RowBox[{"2", "\[Mu]", " ",
        RowBox[{"n",
         RowBox[{"(",
          RowBox[{"n", "+", "1"}], ")"}]}], " ",
        RowBox[{"zn", "/",
         RowBox[{"r", "^", "2"}]}]}]}], ",",
      RowBox[{"2", "\[Mu]",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"(",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"k", " ", "znp"}], "-",
          RowBox[{"zn", "/", "r"}]}], ")"}], "/", "r"}]}]}], "}"}]}],
   ";"}]}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", " ",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     "S", "-", "wave", " ", "fields", " ", "from", " ", "\[Psi]"}], "=",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"zn",
      RowBox[{"(", "kr", ")"}]}], " ", "Pn"}]}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"sF", "[",
     RowBox[{
     "n_", ",", "k_", ",", "r_", ",", "\[Mu]_", ",", "zn_", ",",
      "znp_"}], "]"}], ":=",
    RowBox[{"Module", "[",
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"{",
       RowBox[{"nn1", ",", "z"}], "}"}], ",",
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"nn1", "=",
        RowBox[{"n",
         RowBox[{"(",
          RowBox[{"n", "+", "1"}], ")"}]}]}], ";",
       RowBox[{"z", "=",
        RowBox[{"k", " ", "r"}]}], ";",
       RowBox[{"{",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"nn1", " ",
          RowBox[{"zn", "/", "r"}]}], ",",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"(",
           RowBox[{"zn", "+",
            RowBox[{"z", " ", "znp"}]}], ")"}], "/", "r"}], ",",
         RowBox[{"2", "\[Mu]", " ", "nn1",
          RowBox[{"(",
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{"k", " ",
             RowBox[{"znp", "/", "r"}]}], "-",
            RowBox[{"zn", "/",
             RowBox[{"r", "^", "2"}]}]}], ")"}]}], ",",
         RowBox[{"\[Mu]",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"(",
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{
              RowBox[{"(",
               RowBox[{
                RowBox[{"2", "nn1"}], "-", "2", "-",
                RowBox[{"z", "^", "2"}]}], ")"}], "zn"}], "-",
             RowBox[{"2", "z", " ", "znp"}]}], ")"}], "/",
           RowBox[{"r", "^", "2"}]}]}]}], "}"}]}]}], "]"}]}],
   ";"}]}]}], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[9]:=",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0003-0001-0001-000000000003"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", " ",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     "Solve", " ", "the", " ", "4", "\[Times]4", " ", "Mie", " ", "boundary",
      " ", "problem", " ", "for", " ", "order", " ", "n"}], ",", "\n",
    "   ",
    RowBox[{
     "using", " ", "exact", " ", "Bessel", " ", "functions", " ",
     RowBox[{"(",
      RowBox[{"not", " ", "static", " ", "limits"}], ")"}]}], ",", "\n",
    "   ",
    RowBox[{
     "then", " ", "Series", " ", "expand", " ", "in", " ", "\[Omega]", " ",
     "to", " ", "extract", " ", "the", " ", "static", " ", "leading", " ",
     "coefficient"}]}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"staticEn", "[", "n_Integer", "]"}], ":=",
    RowBox[{"Module", "[", "\n",
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"{",
       RowBox[{
       "a", ",", "w", ",",
        "kPo", ",", "kSo", ",", "kPi", ",", "kSi", ",",
        "\[Alpha]o", ",", "\[Beta]o", ",", "\[Alpha]i", ",", "\[Beta]i",
        ",", "\[Rho]i", ",", "\n",
        "zPo", ",", "zSo", ",", "zPi", ",", "zSi", ",", "\n",
        "jPo", ",", "jPop", ",", "hPo", ",", "hPop", ",", "\n",
        "jSo", ",", "jSop", ",", "hSo", ",", "hSop", ",", "\n",
        "jPi", ",", "jPip", ",", "jSi", ",", "jSip", ",", "\n",
        "scP", ",", "scS", ",", "inP", ",", "inS", ",", "icP", ",", "\n",
        "mat", ",", "rhs", ",", "coeff", ",",
        "anLead", ",", "anBorn", ",", "en"}], "}"}], ",",
      "\n", "\n",
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"a", "=", "1"}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"(*", " ", "Wavespeeds", " ", "*)"}], "\n",
       RowBox[{"\[Alpha]o", "=",
        RowBox[{"Sqrt", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"(",
           RowBox[{"\[Lambda]0", "+",
            RowBox[{"2", "\[Mu]0"}]}], ")"}], "/", "\[Rho]0"}], "]"}]}],
       ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"\[Beta]o", "=",
        RowBox[{"Sqrt", "[",
         RowBox[{"\[Mu]0", "/", "\[Rho]0"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"\[Rho]i", "=",
        RowBox[{"\[Rho]0", "+", "d\[Rho]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"\[Alpha]i", "=",
        RowBox[{"Sqrt", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"(",
           RowBox[{"\[Lambda]1", "+",
            RowBox[{"2", "\[Mu]1"}]}], ")"}], "/", "\[Rho]i"}], "]"}]}],
       ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"\[Beta]i", "=",
        RowBox[{"Sqrt", "[",
         RowBox[{"\[Mu]1", "/", "\[Rho]i"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"(*", " ",
        RowBox[{"Wavenumbers", " ",
         RowBox[{"(",
          RowBox[{"symbolic", " ", "in", " ", "w"}], ")"}]}], " ", "*)"}],
       "\n",
       RowBox[{"kPo", "=",
        RowBox[{"w", "/", "\[Alpha]o"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"kSo", "=",
        RowBox[{"w", "/", "\[Beta]o"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"kPi", "=",
        RowBox[{"w", "/", "\[Alpha]i"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"kSi", "=",
        RowBox[{"w", "/", "\[Beta]i"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"zPo", "=",
        RowBox[{"kPo", " ", "a"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"zSo", "=",
        RowBox[{"kSo", " ", "a"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"zPi", "=",
        RowBox[{"kPi", " ", "a"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"zSi", "=",
        RowBox[{"kSi", " ", "a"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"(*", " ",
        RowBox[{
         "Bessel", " ", "functions", " ", "using", " ", "built", "-",
         RowBox[{"in", " ", "SphericalBesselJ", "/", "SphericalHankelH1"}]}],
         " ", "*)"}], "\n",
       RowBox[{"jPo", "=",
        RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "zPo"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"jPop", "=",
        RowBox[{"D", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
           RowBox[{"n", ",", "zz"}], "]"}], ",", "zz"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"jPop", "=",
        RowBox[{"jPop", "/.",
         RowBox[{"zz", "->", "zPo"}]}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"hPo", "=",
        RowBox[{"SphericalHankelH1", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "zPo"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"hPop", "=",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"D", "[",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"SphericalHankelH1", "[",
            RowBox[{"n", ",", "zz"}], "]"}], ",", "zz"}], "]"}], "/.",
         RowBox[{"zz", "->", "zPo"}]}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"jSo", "=",
        RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "zSo"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"jSop", "=",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"D", "[",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
            RowBox[{"n", ",", "zz"}], "]"}], ",", "zz"}], "]"}], "/.",
         RowBox[{"zz", "->", "zSo"}]}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"hSo", "=",
        RowBox[{"SphericalHankelH1", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "zSo"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"hSop", "=",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"D", "[",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"SphericalHankelH1", "[",
            RowBox[{"n", ",", "zz"}], "]"}], ",", "zz"}], "]"}], "/.",
         RowBox[{"zz", "->", "zSo"}]}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"jPi", "=",
        RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "zPi"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"jPip", "=",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"D", "[",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
            RowBox[{"n", ",", "zz"}], "]"}], ",", "zz"}], "]"}], "/.",
         RowBox[{"zz", "->", "zPi"}]}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"jSi", "=",
        RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "zSi"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"jSip", "=",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"D", "[",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
            RowBox[{"n", ",", "zz"}], "]"}], ",", "zz"}], "]"}], "/.",
         RowBox[{"zz", "->", "zSi"}]}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"(*", " ",
        RowBox[{"Field", " ", "vectors"}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
       RowBox[{"scP", "=",
        RowBox[{"pF", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "kPo", ",", "a", ",", "\[Lambda]0", ",",
          "\[Mu]0", ",", "hPo", ",", "hPop"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"scS", "=",
        RowBox[{"sF", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "kSo", ",", "a", ",", "\[Mu]0", ",",
          "hSo", ",", "hSop"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"inP", "=",
        RowBox[{"pF", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "kPi", ",", "a", ",", "\[Lambda]1", ",",
          "\[Mu]1", ",", "jPi", ",", "jPip"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"inS", "=",
        RowBox[{"sF", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "kSi", ",", "a", ",", "\[Mu]1", ",",
          "jSi", ",", "jSip"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"icP", "=",
        RowBox[{"pF", "[",
         RowBox[{"n", ",", "kPo", ",", "a", ",", "\[Lambda]0", ",",
          "\[Mu]0", ",", "jPo", ",", "jPop"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"(*", " ",
        RowBox[{"4", "\[Times]4", " ", "boundary", " ", "matrix"}], " ",
        "*)"}], "\n",
       RowBox[{"mat", "=",
        RowBox[{"Transpose", "[",
         RowBox[{"{",
          RowBox[{"scP", ",", "scS", ",",
           RowBox[{"-", "inP"}], ",",
           RowBox[{"-", "inS"}]}], "}"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"(*", " ",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Incident", " ", "RHS"}], ":", " ",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"-",
           RowBox[{"(",
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{"(",
              RowBox[{
               RowBox[{"2", "n"}], "+", "1"}], ")"}],
             RowBox[{
              RowBox[{"I", "^", "n"}], "/",
              RowBox[{"(",
               RowBox[{"I", " ", "kPo"}], ")"}]}]}], ")"}]}],
          " ", "icP"}]}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
       RowBox[{"coeff", "=",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"(",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"2", "n"}], "+", "1"}], ")"}],
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"I", "^", "n"}], "/",
          RowBox[{"(",
           RowBox[{"I", " ", "kPo"}], ")"}]}]}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"rhs", "=",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"-", "coeff"}], " ", "icP"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"(*", " ",
        RowBox[{
         "Series", " ", "expand", " ", "matrix", " ", "entries", " ", "to",
         " ", "Laurent", " ", "polynomials", " ", "then", " ", "Limit"}],
        " ", "*)"}], "\n",
       RowBox[{"mat", "=",
        RowBox[{"Map", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"Function", "[",
           RowBox[{"x", ",",
            RowBox[{"Normal", "[",
             RowBox[{"Series", "[",
              RowBox[{"x", ",",
               RowBox[{"{",
                RowBox[{"w", ",", "0", ",",
                 RowBox[{
                  RowBox[{"2", "n"}], "+", "6"}]}], "}"}]}], "]"}],
             "]"}]}], "]"}], ",", "mat", ",",
          RowBox[{"{", "2", "}"}]}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"rhs", "=",
        RowBox[{"Map", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"Function", "[",
           RowBox[{"x", ",",
            RowBox[{"Normal", "[",
             RowBox[{"Series", "[",
              RowBox[{"x", ",",
               RowBox[{"{",
                RowBox[{"w", ",", "0", ",",
                 RowBox[{
                  RowBox[{"2", "n"}], "+", "6"}]}], "}"}]}], "]"}],
             "]"}]}], "]"}], ",", "rhs"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"anLead", "=",
        RowBox[{"Cancel", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"Det", "[",
           RowBox[{"Transpose", "[",
            RowBox[{"{",
             RowBox[{"rhs", ",",
              RowBox[{"mat", "[",
               RowBox[{"[",
                RowBox[{"All", ",", "2"}], "]"}], "]"}], ",",
              RowBox[{"mat", "[",
               RowBox[{"[",
                RowBox[{"All", ",", "3"}], "]"}], "]"}], ",",
              RowBox[{"mat", "[",
               RowBox[{"[",
                RowBox[{"All", ",", "4"}], "]"}], "]"}]}], "}"}], "]"}],
           "]"}], "/",
          RowBox[{"Det", "[", "mat", "]"}]}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       "\n",
       RowBox[{"(*", " ",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Born", " ", "limit"}], ":", " ",
         RowBox[{
          "linearize", " ", "in", " ", "contrasts"}]}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
       RowBox[{"anBorn", "=",
        RowBox[{"Simplify", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"Normal", "[",
           RowBox[{"Series", "[",
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{"anLead", "/.",
              RowBox[{"{",
               RowBox[{
                RowBox[{"d\[Lambda]", "->",
                 RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", " ", "d\[Lambda]"}]}], ",",
                RowBox[{"d\[Mu]", "->",
                 RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", " ", "d\[Mu]"}]}], ",",
                RowBox[{"d\[Rho]", "->",
                 RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", " ", "d\[Rho]"}]}]}], "}"}]}], ",",
             RowBox[{"{",
              RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", ",", "0", ",", "1"}], "}"}]}], "]"}],
           "]"}], "/.",
          RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", "->", "1"}]}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
       RowBox[{"(*", " ",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Concentration", " ", "factor", " ", "E_n"}], " ", "=",
         " ",
         RowBox[{"full", "/", "Born"}]}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
       RowBox[{"en", "=",
        RowBox[{"Simplify", "[",
         RowBox[{"Limit", "[",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"anLead", "/", "anBorn"}], ",",
           RowBox[{"w", "->", "0"}]}], "]"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
       RowBox[{"{",
        RowBox[{"en", ",", "anLead", ",", "anBorn"}], "}"}]}]}], "\n",
     "]"}]}], ";"}]}]}], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[11]:=",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0003-0001-0001-000000000004"]
}, Open  ]],

(* ===== Section 3: n=0 Monopole ===== *)

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["3. n=0 Monopole (2\[Times]2 System)", "Section",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0004-0001-0001-000000000001"],

Cell["\<\
The monopole (n=0) is purely P-wave with no S-wave coupling, giving a \
2\[Times]2 system. Solve separately.\
\>", "Text",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0004-0001-0001-000000000002"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"staticE0", "[", "]"}], ":=",
   RowBox[{"Module", "[", "\n",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"{",
      RowBox[{
      "a", ",", "w", ",",
       "kPo", ",", "kPi", ",",
       "\[Alpha]o", ",", "\[Alpha]i", ",", "\[Rho]i", ",",
       "zPo", ",", "zPi", ",", "\n",
       "jPo", ",", "jPop", ",", "hPo", ",", "hPop", ",",
       "jPi", ",", "jPip", ",", "\n",
       "scP", ",", "inP", ",", "icP", ",",
       "M2", ",", "rhs2", ",",
       "a0Lead", ",", "a0Born", ",", "e0"}], "}"}], ",",
     "\n", "\n",
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"a", "=", "1"}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"\[Alpha]o", "=",
       RowBox[{"Sqrt", "[",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"(",
          RowBox[{"\[Lambda]0", "+",
           RowBox[{"2", "\[Mu]0"}]}], ")"}], "/", "\[Rho]0"}], "]"}]}],
      ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"\[Rho]i", "=",
       RowBox[{"\[Rho]0", "+", "d\[Rho]"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"\[Alpha]i", "=",
       RowBox[{"Sqrt", "[",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"(",
          RowBox[{"\[Lambda]1", "+",
           RowBox[{"2", "\[Mu]1"}]}], ")"}], "/", "\[Rho]i"}], "]"}]}],
      ";", "\n", "\n",
      RowBox[{"kPo", "=",
       RowBox[{"w", "/", "\[Alpha]o"}]}], ";",
      RowBox[{"kPi", "=",
       RowBox[{"w", "/", "\[Alpha]i"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"zPo", "=",
       RowBox[{"kPo", " ", "a"}]}], ";",
      RowBox[{"zPi", "=",
       RowBox[{"kPi", " ", "a"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
      RowBox[{"(*", " ",
       RowBox[{
        "Bessel", " ", "functions", " ", "via", " ", "built", "-", "ins"}],
       " ", "*)"}], "\n",
      RowBox[{"jPo", "=",
       RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
        RowBox[{"0", ",", "zPo"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"jPop", "=",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"D", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
           RowBox[{"0", ",", "zz"}], "]"}], ",", "zz"}], "]"}], "/.",
        RowBox[{"zz", "->", "zPo"}]}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"hPo", "=",
       RowBox[{"SphericalHankelH1", "[",
        RowBox[{"0", ",", "zPo"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"hPop", "=",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"D", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"SphericalHankelH1", "[",
           RowBox[{"0", ",", "zz"}], "]"}], ",", "zz"}], "]"}], "/.",
        RowBox[{"zz", "->", "zPo"}]}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"jPi", "=",
       RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
        RowBox[{"0", ",", "zPi"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"jPip", "=",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"D", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"SphericalBesselJ", "[",
           RowBox[{"0", ",", "zz"}], "]"}], ",", "zz"}], "]"}], "/.",
        RowBox[{"zz", "->", "zPi"}]}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
      RowBox[{"(*", " ",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{
         "For", " ", "n", "=", "0"}], ":", " ",
        RowBox[{
         "only", " ", "ur", " ", "and", " ", "srr", " ", "matter"}]}], " ",
       "*)"}], "\n",
      RowBox[{"scP", "=",
       RowBox[{"pF", "[",
        RowBox[{"0", ",", "kPo", ",", "a", ",", "\[Lambda]0", ",",
         "\[Mu]0", ",", "hPo", ",", "hPop"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"inP", "=",
       RowBox[{"pF", "[",
        RowBox[{"0", ",", "kPi", ",", "a", ",", "\[Lambda]1", ",",
         "\[Mu]1", ",", "jPi", ",", "jPip"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"icP", "=",
       RowBox[{"pF", "[",
        RowBox[{"0", ",", "kPo", ",", "a", ",", "\[Lambda]0", ",",
         "\[Mu]0", ",", "jPo", ",", "jPop"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
      RowBox[{"M2", "=",
       RowBox[{"{",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"{",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"scP", "[",
            RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}], ",",
           RowBox[{"-",
            RowBox[{"inP", "[",
             RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]}]}], "}"}], ",",
         RowBox[{"{",
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"scP", "[",
            RowBox[{"[", "3", "]"}], "]"}], ",",
           RowBox[{"-",
            RowBox[{"inP", "[",
             RowBox[{"[", "3", "]"}], "]"}]}]}], "}"}]}], "}"}]}], ";",
      "\n",
      RowBox[{"rhs2", "=",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"-", "1"}], "/",
         RowBox[{"(",
          RowBox[{"I", " ", "kPo"}], ")"}]}],
        RowBox[{"{",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"icP", "[",
           RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}], ",",
          RowBox[{"icP", "[",
           RowBox[{"[", "3", "]"}], "]"}]}], "}"}]}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
      RowBox[{"(*", " ",
       RowBox[{
        "Series", " ", "expand", " ", "matrix", " ", "entries", " ", "to",
        " ", "Laurent", " ", "polynomials", " ", "then", " ", "Limit"}],
       " ", "*)"}], "\n",
      RowBox[{"M2", "=",
       RowBox[{"Map", "[",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Function", "[",
          RowBox[{"x", ",",
           RowBox[{"Normal", "[",
            RowBox[{"Series", "[",
             RowBox[{"x", ",",
              RowBox[{"{",
               RowBox[{"w", ",", "0", ",", "6"}], "}"}]}], "]"}],
            "]"}]}], "]"}], ",", "M2", ",",
         RowBox[{"{", "2", "}"}]}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"rhs2", "=",
       RowBox[{"Map", "[",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Function", "[",
          RowBox[{"x", ",",
           RowBox[{"Normal", "[",
            RowBox[{"Series", "[",
             RowBox[{"x", ",",
              RowBox[{"{",
               RowBox[{"w", ",", "0", ",", "6"}], "}"}]}], "]"}],
            "]"}]}], "]"}], ",", "rhs2"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"a0Lead", "=",
       RowBox[{"Cancel", "[",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Det", "[",
          RowBox[{"Transpose", "[",
           RowBox[{"{",
            RowBox[{"rhs2", ",",
             RowBox[{"M2", "[",
              RowBox[{"[",
               RowBox[{"All", ",", "2"}], "]"}], "]"}]}], "}"}], "]"}],
          "]"}], "/",
         RowBox[{"Det", "[", "M2", "]"}]}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
      RowBox[{"(*", " ",
       RowBox[{"Born", " ", "limit"}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
      RowBox[{"a0Born", "=",
       RowBox[{"Simplify", "[",
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Normal", "[",
          RowBox[{"Series", "[",
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{"a0Lead", "/.",
             RowBox[{"{",
              RowBox[{
               RowBox[{"d\[Lambda]", "->",
                RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", " ", "d\[Lambda]"}]}], ",",
               RowBox[{"d\[Mu]", "->",
                RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", " ", "d\[Mu]"}]}], ",",
               RowBox[{"d\[Rho]", "->",
                RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", " ", "d\[Rho]"}]}]}], "}"}]}], ",",
            RowBox[{"{",
             RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", ",", "0", ",", "1"}], "}"}]}], "]"}],
          "]"}], "/.",
         RowBox[{"\[Epsilon]", "->", "1"}]}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n", "\n",
      RowBox[{"e0", "=",
       RowBox[{"Simplify", "[",
        RowBox[{"Limit", "[",
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"a0Lead", "/", "a0Born"}], ",",
          RowBox[{"w", "->", "0"}]}], "]"}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
      RowBox[{"{",
       RowBox[{"e0", ",", "a0Lead", ",", "a0Born"}], "}"}]}]}], "\n",
    "]"}]}], ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"{",
    RowBox[{"e0Sym", ",", "a0Red", ",", "a0Bor"}], "}"}], "=",
   RowBox[{"staticE0", "[", "]"}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   RowBox[{"\"\<E_0 (symbolic) = \>\"", ",", "e0Sym"}], "]"}],
  ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", " ",
   RowBox[{"Verify", " ", "against", " ", "classical"}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"\[Alpha]E", "=",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"3", "K0"}], "/",
     RowBox[{"(",
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"3", "K0"}], "+",
       RowBox[{"4", "\[Mu]0"}]}], ")"}]}]}], ";"}]}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"e0Classical", "=",
   RowBox[{"K0", "/",
    RowBox[{"(",
     RowBox[{"K0", "+",
      RowBox[{"\[Alpha]E", " ", "dK"}]}], ")"}]}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   RowBox[{"\"\<E_0 match classical: \>\"", ",",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Simplify", "[",
      RowBox[{"e0Sym", "-", "e0Classical"}], "]"}], "===", "0"}]}], "]"}],
  ";"}]}], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[12]:=",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0004-0001-0001-000000000003"]
}, Open  ]],

(* ===== Section 4: n=1 through n=5 ===== *)

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["4. Compute E_1 through E_5", "Section",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0005-0001-0001-000000000001"],

Cell["\<\
Compute concentration factors for multipole orders n=1 through 5 using the \
general 4\[Times]4 solver.\
\>", "Text",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0005-0001-0001-000000000002"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Do", "[", "\n",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"{",
       RowBox[{"eSym", ",", "aRed", ",", "aBor"}], "}"}], "=",
      RowBox[{"staticEn", "[", "nn", "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"enRes", "[", "nn", "]"}], "=",
      RowBox[{"{",
       RowBox[{"eSym", ",", "aRed", ",", "aBor"}], "}"}]}], ";", "\n",
     RowBox[{"Print", "[",
      RowBox[{"\"\<E_\>\"", ",", "nn", ",", "\"\< = \>\"", ",", "eSym"}],
      "]"}], ";"}], ",", "\n",
    RowBox[{"{",
     RowBox[{"nn", ",", "1", ",", "5"}], "}"}]}], "]"}], ";"}]}], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[18]:=",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0005-0001-0001-000000000003"]
}, Open  ]],

(* ===== Section 5: Verify Known Results ===== *)

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["5. Verification of Known Results", "Section",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0006-0001-0001-000000000001"],

Cell["\<\
Verify that E_0, E_1, E_2 match the classical Eshelby theory:
  E_0 = K_0/(K_0 + \[Alpha]_E \[CapitalDelta]K) with \[Alpha]_E = \
3K_0/(3K_0+4\[Mu]_0)
  E_1 = 1 (no static density renormalization)
  E_2 = 1/(1 + \[Beta]_E \[CapitalDelta]\[Mu]/\[Mu]_0) with \[Beta]_E = \
6(K_0+2\[Mu]_0)/(5(3K_0+4\[Mu]_0))\
\>", "Text",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0006-0001-0001-000000000002"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[Beta]E", "=",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"6",
     RowBox[{"(",
      RowBox[{"K0", "+",
       RowBox[{"2", "\[Mu]0"}]}], ")"}]}], "/",
    RowBox[{"(",
     RowBox[{"5",
      RowBox[{"(",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"3", "K0"}], "+",
        RowBox[{"4", "\[Mu]0"}]}], ")"}]}], ")"}]}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"e2Classical", "=",
   RowBox[{"1", "/",
    RowBox[{"(",
     RowBox[{"1", "+",
      RowBox[{"\[Beta]E", " ",
       RowBox[{"d\[Mu]", "/", "\[Mu]0"}]}]}], ")"}]}]}], ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"e1Sym", "=",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"enRes", "[", "1", "]"}], "[",
    RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   RowBox[{"\"\<E_1 = \>\"", ",", "e1Sym", ",",
    "\"\<  (should be 1)\>\""}], "]"}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   RowBox[{"\"\<E_1 == 1: \>\"", ",",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Simplify", "[",
      RowBox[{"e1Sym", "-", "1"}], "]"}], "===", "0"}]}], "]"}],
  ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"e2Sym", "=",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"enRes", "[", "2", "]"}], "[",
    RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   RowBox[{"\"\<\\nE_2 (symbolic) = \>\"", ",", "e2Sym"}], "]"}],
  ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   RowBox[{"\"\<E_2 (classical) = \>\"", ",",
    RowBox[{"Simplify", "[", "e2Classical", "]"}]}], "]"}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   RowBox[{"\"\<E_2 match: \>\"", ",",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Simplify", "[",
      RowBox[{"e2Sym", "-", "e2Classical"}], "]"}], "===", "0"}]}], "]"}],
  ";"}]}], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[19]:=",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0006-0001-0001-000000000003"]
}, Open  ]],

(* ===== Section 6: Numerical Validation ===== *)

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["6. Numerical Validation Against Python", "Section",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0007-0001-0001-000000000001"],

Cell["\<\
Substitute numerical test parameters matching the Python test suite and \
compare against compute_static_eshelby_factors output.\
\>", "Text",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0007-0001-0001-000000000002"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[Alpha]num", "=", "5000"}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[Beta]num", "=", "3000"}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[Rho]num", "=", "2500"}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[Lambda]num", "=",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"\[Rho]num", " ",
     RowBox[{"\[Alpha]num", "^", "2"}]}], "-",
    RowBox[{"2", "\[Rho]num", " ",
     RowBox[{"\[Beta]num", "^", "2"}]}]}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[Mu]num", "=",
   RowBox[{"\[Rho]num", " ",
    RowBox[{"\[Beta]num", "^", "2"}]}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"d\[Lambda]num", "=",
   RowBox[{"2", " ",
    RowBox[{"10", "^", "9"}]}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"d\[Mu]num", "=",
   RowBox[{"10", "^", "9"}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"d\[Rho]num", "=", "100"}], ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"numRules", "=",
   RowBox[{"{",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"\[Lambda]0", "->", "\[Lambda]num"}], ",",
     RowBox[{"\[Mu]0", "->", "\[Mu]num"}], ",",
     RowBox[{"\[Rho]0", "->", "\[Rho]num"}], ",", "\n",
     RowBox[{"d\[Lambda]", "->", "d\[Lambda]num"}], ",",
     RowBox[{"d\[Mu]", "->", "d\[Mu]num"}], ",",
     RowBox[{"d\[Rho]", "->", "d\[Rho]num"}]}], "}"}]}], ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", " ",
   RowBox[{"Python", " ", "reference", " ", "values"}], " ", "*)"}], "\n",
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"pyRef", "=",
    RowBox[{"{",
     RowBox[{
     "0.9590828991", ",", "1.0000029890", ",", "0.9784326389", ",",
      "0.9748482740", ",", "0.9734666883", ",", "0.9727525952"}], "}"}]}],
   ";"}]}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[", "\"\<=== Numerical Validation ===\>\"", "]"}],
  ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"e0Val", "=",
   RowBox[{"N", "[",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"e0Sym", "/.", "numRules"}], ",", "10"}], "]"}]}], ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   RowBox[{"\"\<E_0 = \>\"", ",", "e0Val", ",",
    "\"\<  (Python: \>\"", ",",
    RowBox[{"pyRef", "[",
     RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}], ",", "\"\<)\>\""}], "]"}],
  ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Do", "[", "\n",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"eVal", "=",
      RowBox[{"N", "[",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"enRes", "[", "nn", "]"}], "[",
          RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}], "/.", "numRules"}], ",", "10"}],
       "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
     RowBox[{"Print", "[",
      RowBox[{"\"\<E_\>\"", ",", "nn", ",", "\"\< = \>\"", ",", "eVal",
       ",", "\"\<  (Python: \>\"", ",",
       RowBox[{"pyRef", "[",
        RowBox[{"[",
         RowBox[{"nn", "+", "1"}], "]"}], "]"}], ",", "\"\<)\>\""}],
      "]"}], ";"}], ",", "\n",
    RowBox[{"{",
     RowBox[{"nn", ",", "1", ",", "5"}], "}"}]}], "]"}], ";"}]}], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[28]:=",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0007-0001-0001-000000000003"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   "\"\<\\n=== Agreement Check (|error| < 1e-4) ===\>\"", "]"}],
  ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"allPass", "=", "True"}], ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"e0v", "=",
   RowBox[{"N", "[",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"e0Sym", "/.", "numRules"}], ",", "15"}], "]"}]}],
  ";"}], "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"If", "[",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Abs", "[",
      RowBox[{"e0v", "-",
       RowBox[{"pyRef", "[",
        RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]}], "]"}], ">",
     RowBox[{"10", "^",
      RowBox[{"-", "4"}]}]}], ",",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Print", "[",
      RowBox[{"\"\<FAIL E_0: err=\>\"", ",",
       RowBox[{"Abs", "[",
        RowBox[{"e0v", "-",
         RowBox[{"pyRef", "[",
          RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]}], "]"}]}], "]"}], ";",
     RowBox[{"allPass", "=", "False"}]}], ",",
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"Print", "[", "\"\<PASS E_0\>\"", "]"}], ";"}]}], "]"}],
  ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Do", "[", "\n",
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"ev", "=",
      RowBox[{"N", "[",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"enRes", "[", "nn", "]"}], "[",
          RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}], "/.", "numRules"}], ",", "15"}],
       "]"}]}], ";", "\n",
     RowBox[{"If", "[",
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"Abs", "[",
         RowBox[{"ev", "-",
          RowBox[{"pyRef", "[",
           RowBox[{"[",
            RowBox[{"nn", "+", "1"}], "]"}], "]"}]}], "]"}], ">",
        RowBox[{"10", "^",
         RowBox[{"-", "4"}]}]}], ",",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"Print", "[",
         RowBox[{"\"\<FAIL E_\>\"", ",", "nn", ",",
          "\"\<: err=\>\"", ",",
          RowBox[{"Abs", "[",
           RowBox[{"ev", "-",
            RowBox[{"pyRef", "[",
             RowBox[{"[",
              RowBox[{"nn", "+", "1"}], "]"}], "]"}]}], "]"}]}], "]"}], ";",
        RowBox[{"allPass", "=", "False"}]}], ",",
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"Print", "[",
         RowBox[{"\"\<PASS E_\>\"", ",", "nn"}], "]"}], ";"}]}], "]"}],
     ";"}], ",", "\n",
    RowBox[{"{",
     RowBox[{"nn", ",", "1", ",", "5"}], "}"}]}], "]"}], ";"}], "\n", "\n",
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"Print", "[",
   RowBox[{"\"\<\\nAll tests passed: \>\"", ",", "allPass"}], "]"}],
  ";"}]}], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[42]:=",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0007-0001-0001-000000000004"]
}, Open  ]],

(* ===== Section 7: Summary ===== *)

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["7. Summary", "Section",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0008-0001-0001-000000000001"],

Cell["\<\
The static Mie boundary problem for a sphere reduces to a purely algebraic \
system when the Bessel functions are Series-expanded in \[Omega]. Using \
Mathematica\[CloseCurlyQuote]s built-in SphericalBesselJ and \
SphericalHankelH1, we extract the leading-order scattering coefficient at \
each multipole order n, then form the ratio E_n = full/Born.

Results:
  E_0 = K_0/(K_0 + \[Alpha]_E \[CapitalDelta]K)      [monopole/bulk modulus]
  E_1 = 1                                         [dipole/density]
  E_2 = 1/(1 + \[Beta]_E \[CapitalDelta]\[Mu]/\[Mu]_0)   [quadrupole/shear \
modulus]
  E_3, E_4, E_5: new closed-form rational functions

Key observations:
\[Bullet] E_1 = 1 exactly: the dipole mode is purely inertial.
\[Bullet] E_n for n \[GreaterEqual] 2 depends only on \[CapitalDelta]\[Mu], \
not \[CapitalDelta]\[Lambda] or \[CapitalDelta]\[Rho].
\[Bullet] All E_n are real in the static limit.
\[Bullet] E_n \[Rule] 1 as \[CapitalDelta]\[Mu] \[Rule] 0.
\[Bullet] Numerical values match Python to \[PlusMinus]10^-4.\
\>", "Text",
 ExpressionUUID->"b1c2d3e4-0008-0001-0001-000000000002"]
}, Open  ]]

}, Open  ]]
},
